Step 1 
    Insert a attach field in your Power Apps application 

Step 2
    Insert a button. In this component paste the first code. 
    It is response for runs each item on attach field and save the file name and component.

Step 3
    Insert a gallery. In this component insert the first collection and on image gallery image component write 
    ThisItem.base64 and on label insert ThisItem.Name.

Step 4
    Paste the Second Code. This element will read and get all records on gallery and transfrom each of them for base64.

Step 5
    Paste the Third Code. It is been used for crop the Mime Type of each record. It is not mandatory that you use it. 